&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL1JhdmVuU3lzdGVtL2hhYS9yZWxlYXNlcy9kb3dubG9hZC8yLjQuNC9oYWFtYWluLmJpbg==&#34;&gt;haamain.bin&lt;/span&gt; 、 &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL1N1cGVySG91c2UvZXNwLW9wZW4tcnRvcy9yYXcvbWFzdGVyL2Jvb3Rsb2FkZXIvZmlybXdhcmVfcHJlYnVpbHQvcmJvb3QuYmlu&#34;&gt;rboot.bin&lt;/span&gt; 、 &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL1N1cGVySG91c2UvZXNwLW9wZW4tcnRvcy9yYXcvbWFzdGVyL2Jvb3Rsb2FkZXIvZmlybXdhcmVfcHJlYnVpbHQvYmxhbmtfY29uZmlnLmJpbg==&#34;&gt;blank_config.bin&lt;/span&gt; 这里三个文件都需要下载 &lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL1JhdmVuU3lzdGVtL2VzcC1ob21la2l0LWRldmljZXM=&#34;&gt;项目地址&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
